## Persistent Lessons (UI)

> Broader **UI** patterns noticed over time — not single-incident fixes. Add entries when a recurring class of problem appears.

**Empirical UI patterns (trial-and-error resolutions):** When the correct control or sequence is only found after **multiple failed attempts** (e.g. wrong ref, hidden elements, env timing), append a dated entry here with **what failed**, **what worked**, and **how to confirm success** in the next snapshot. On future runs, **read this section before interacting** with similar pages so the same trial-and-error path is skipped. Do not delete prior entries.

---

